# Keep the built image to just what the mock actually serves. The server's KEEP() filter only serves
# .c4/.likec4/.likec4.snap under repos/, so the curated fixtures' provenance docs (NOTICE, PROVENANCE.md)
# are dead weight baked into the image — exclude them from the build context rather than COPY'ing them in.
# Cosmetic (image size only): the running stack is unaffected until the next `up -d --build`.
**/*.md
**/NOTICE
